files.patch:
@@ -32,0 +32,11 @@
+// glibc <sys/sysmacros.h> which may get brought in via <sys/types.h>
+// defines the macros minor and major. These keywords are central to
+// the GC algorithm. These macros are undefined here so the code may
+// use minor and major.
+#ifdef minor
+#undef minor
+#endif
+#ifdef major
+#undef major
+#endif
+
